name: Bugfixes
body:
Changelog:
- Fixed bug with login token
- Updated restclient to 2.0.0

name: Major project rework
body:
Project was reworked an internal backends and project structure changed. The most important changes/additions are:
- Synchronization backend changed, see README.md
- Fixed bugs preventing the app from doing its job
- Added possibility to log in to select animes from the history
- Settings are now synchronized
- Fine control over what kind of relations to synchronize

Google Play: https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=de.skycoder42.anirem
AUR: https://aur.archlinux.org/packages/anirem/
AUR git: https://aur.archlinux.org/packages/anirem-git/
